text: This Hour Has 22 Minutes is a Canadian comedy television series created by Mary Walsh, Cathy Jones, Michael Donovan, Jack Kellum, Gerald Lunz and George Anthony. In Canada reruns are shown on The Comedy Network and new episodes are shown on Canadian Broadcasting Corporation. On a 2004-05 episode, Carolyn Parrish was shown stomping on a George W. Bush doll and performing voodoo on its head which ultimately lead to her dismissal from the Liberal caucus. ==References== ==Other websites== *This Hour Has 22 Minutes at cbc.ca Category:1993 Canadian television series debuts Category:Canadian television series Category:Comedy television series Category:English-language television programs
